    "body": "## Summary\n- remove brittle Boomer Step 4.4B dependence on the obsolete historical dev-check cache-bust literal\n- verify the actually loaded same-origin `dev/dev-checks.js` asset, require a non-empty version query, and confirm the loaded source contains the current Boomer 4.4B buildTag, smokeVersion, and smoke function\n- advance the Boomer 4.4B smoke identity to Fix5 and refresh the dev-check deployment cache-bust\n- preserve existing state/profile/economy/battle/persistence restoration and adversarial safety checks\n\n## Scope\nExactly four files:\n- `AsyncScene/Web/dev/dev-checks.js`\n- `docs/dev/dev-checks.js`\n- `AsyncScene/Web/index.html`\n- `docs/index.html`\n\nNo product copy, gameplay, economy, battle, NPC, state, persistence, `data.js`, `system.js`, memory, selector, or bridge changes.\n\n## Validation\n- selector snapshot `20260722.1`, selected `5.4 / Light`, `IMPLEMENTATION_ALLOWED`\n- exact baseline `052e5e396f62b2a43feb9cae7b0fc3d5534012f2`\n- implementation head `3b2c20baa187ee9e80b3d06b390d98593e1303b8`\n- Boomer 4.4A remains `STATIC_PASS / READY_FOR_RUNTIME_SMOKE`, 147/147 pass, 0 fail, 0 structural\n- focused 4.4B contract proof: obsolete marker removed; wrong path, missing identity, and stale/incompatible source still fail; current loaded artifact contract can pass\n- source/docs mirrors byte-identical\n- node syntax PASS on both dev-check mirrors\n- `git diff --check` PASS\n- Safari runtime acceptance not run; status `PENDING_USER`\n\nNEXT_ACTION after independent integration: `USER_SAFARI_RUNTIME_SMOKE_STAGE6_BOOMER_STEP4_4B`",
